title: A Hawk Landed On My Head (Maya Higa)
itunes:author: Joe Vulpis & Ilya Feddy
itunes:summary:
A hawk lands on my head, surprising her in Africa, and raising $500,000. Todays guest we have Maya Higa, a conservationist/twitch streamer who just opened up her own sanctuary.

Check out Maya on instagram @maya_higa

Video Podcast Channel Here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCChM6tHqj-4FwbG_KdIjKUw follow us on Instagram @lightweightspod // @ilyafeddy // @ughitsjoe
